These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, adventure
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, tennis
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, airplane
1. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
2. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4
3. the person watching adventure movies is the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | 7up  | cola   |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | horror   |
| Sport         | tennis | snowboarding |
| Transport     | quad-bike | airplane    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: peach, carrot
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: scientific, zombie
2 different pets are kept: bird, pony
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, helicopter
1. the owner of the pony is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching scientific movies is the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | peach     | carrot |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | scientific  |
| Pet           | pony         | bird     |
| Transport     | ship   | helicopter    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, coffee
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, journalist
2 different pets are kept: bird, hamster
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the journalist##3
2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the journalist##1
3. the person drinking cola is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | coffee     | cola |
| Job         | journalist | project-manager    |
| Pet         | bird         | hamster        |
| Transport   | jet-ski         | scooter    |

