There 2 different types of food: pear, mango
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, drawing
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, rock
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person eating mango is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the fan of rock is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | cola     | soy-milk |
| Food          | mango   | pear  |
| Hobby         | camping | drawing     |
| Music-Genre   | folk  | rock         |

