.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  freelancer, paramedic
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, french
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, frog
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
2. the french is on the far left or far right##3
3. the paramedic is the brazilian##1
4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | paramedic | freelancer    |
| Nationality   | brazilian       | french |
| Pet           | hedgehog         | frog    |
| Sport         | swimming    | weightlifting   |

